metadata.name: STILL HERE #01
metadata.description:
Still here, shackled deep in a mental estate of noir thewiness. 
Bound by these circumstances that circumscribe my creative introspection, circumstances strategically structured to annihilate my thought process. 
Scenes, plots, Acts, episodes, props, sets, crafted to suppress, distort and discombobulate. 
Nonetheless, as you can see, I am still here, ingurgitating challenges, trials, discontentment, chauvinism. 
I have risen above these synonyms of debacle as these tribulations only triggered a melanin powered genius of immeasurable adroitness. 

I AM STILL HERE!
